@startuml feedback_flow_v1_0
actor User
participant "UI: FeedbackChat" as UI
participant "API: /api/feedback" as API
participant "Service: Prisma" as DB
database "SQLite/PostgreSQL" as Store

== Initializing Feedback ==
User -> UI: Navigates to Task/Contract Detail
UI -> API: GET /api/feedback?taskId={id} 
UI -> API: (Polling every 5s)
API -> DB: prisma.feedback.findMany({ where: { taskId } })
DB -> Store: SELECT * FROM Feedback
Store --> DB: Results
DB --> API: Feedback data
API --> UI: JSON Response
UI -> User: Display Messages

== Sending Feedback ==
User -> UI: Writes content and clicks Send
UI -> User: (Optimistic UI update)
UI -> API: POST /api/feedback { content, taskId, userId }
API -> DB: prisma.feedback.create({ data })
DB -> Store: INSERT INTO Feedback
Store --> DB: Success
DB --> API: New Feedback object
API --> UI: JSON Response
UI -> User: Final Message State

@enduml
